snippet.title: THE TRAINER - Aiming.Pro New Feature
snippet.description:
The Trainer is the fastest way to improve your aim in the games you love. Through careful analysis and insight we've assembled a progression of drills to improve your aim fast, efficiently, and enjoyably.

https://aiming.pro/#/trainer

No more guessing about what to train and in what order. We've done the hard work for you.
